Trade/Device Name(s): Wondfo Amphetamine Urine Test AMP 500 (Cup, DipCard)
Wondfo Cocaine Urine Test COC 150 (Cup, DipCard)
Wondfo Methamphetamine Urine Test MET 500 (Cup, DipCard)
Regulation Name(s): Cocaine and cocaine metabolite test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Wondfo urine rapid immunochromatographic assays for qualitative detection of amphetamine, cocaine, and methamphetamine using cup and dipcard formats in urine specimens
Indications for Use Summary: OTC rapid qualitative urine tests for amphetamine (AMP 500), cocaine metabolite benzoylecgonine (COC 150), and methamphetamine (MET 500) at specified cutoffs, as preliminary screening devices with confirmatory GC/MS recommended
